Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.28,0:23:17.29,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}隨性挑選著五彩的光線
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.50,0:23:19.53,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}為了協調我們的心跳
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.74,0:23:23.20,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}做自己想做的事情吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:50.02,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1}去海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:57.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:01:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是夏天了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.58,0:02:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是夏天了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.90,0:02:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是夏天了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:05.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是夏天了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:07.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是夏天了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.41,0:02:13.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼如此不必要地強調夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.81,0:02:15.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香  我們去海邊吧  去海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:17.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.77,0:02:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋想去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.04,0:02:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那我們下週日去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.48,0:02:28.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？千秋想去才去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊  你們倆都說想去才…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.27,0:02:35.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對了  得把泳衣找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.12,0:02:39.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來是有陣子沒拿出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.21,0:02:42.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.78,0:02:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找著了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋找著了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.71,0:02:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:02:59.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.25,0:03:01.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有點兒小
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.90,0:03:14.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（緊）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為長高了才穿不上的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.82,0:03:22.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  絕不是變胖了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.26,0:03:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「成長了」這麼便利的字眼是我們的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  我去買新的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.85,0:03:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.46,0:03:33.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而春香準備晚飯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:34.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.53,0:03:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？那我的泳衣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.42,0:03:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心  我們會替你挑的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.70,0:03:49.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩截兒的泳衣就不存在這種問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們根本沒胖
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.66,0:03:54.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.84,0:03:55.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:03:58.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來春香的不僅是上下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左右也分開比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.54,0:04:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:06.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣料分作兩塊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.74,0:04:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但用線繫著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.51,0:04:10.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.34,0:04:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能讓春香姐姐在大庭廣眾之下穿成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:16.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  你太嫩了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.76,0:04:17.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.85,0:04:19.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你根本就不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:20.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.21,0:04:22.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為一名女高中生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:26.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度的裸露都沒有反而不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想想
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.54,0:04:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都穿得很暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:37.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就春香穿著宇航員般厚重的潛水服跳進大海
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.51,0:04:40.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常顯眼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.91,0:04:42.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著大家會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.04,0:04:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你要潛多深？」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:49.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓春香丟人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.46,0:04:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我們能做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:59.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只有替她選一款不至於丟人的布料較少的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.01,0:05:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是初中生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.25,0:05:08.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最接近女高中生的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.60,0:05:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:12.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚的飯菜也非常美味
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.17,0:05:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粗茶淡飯而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:16.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來  夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該讓我看看你買的是怎樣的泳衣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.47,0:05:21.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.23,0:05:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你期待那一天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.12,0:05:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您別這樣～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:42.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.88,0:05:45.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能硬來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  別發出些奇怪的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓春香姐姐丟人  我們選得很賣力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會讓可愛妹妹的努力白費吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨聲真動聽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:25.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  您說得沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.40,0:06:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷彿蕩滌著我們的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.84,0:06:32.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  這雨下幾天了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:35.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  三天了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.88,0:06:37.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  已經三天了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.77,0:06:39.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來明天就是週日的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:41.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就去不成海邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你還說什麼「蕩滌靈魂」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.11,0:06:45.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧這雨現在才這麼涼爽
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.94,0:06:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來的目的也算達成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.85,0:06:54.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種目的現在已經無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.26,0:06:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去海邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:06:58.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  算了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:02.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽著雨聲平靜地度日也不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.37,0:07:04.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.86,0:07:06.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  閉上眼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:11.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聆聽自然那優美的歌聲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:17.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再不停連混凝土都得泡爛了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.40,0:07:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.42,0:07:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  雨雲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.68,0:07:27.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐正犯愁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.86,0:07:29.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓太陽出來  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.30,0:07:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  來做晴天娃娃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.83,0:07:44.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才在嘲笑我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.45,0:07:47.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.81,0:07:49.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  情不自禁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.66,0:07:52.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:54.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我用床單把你給捲起來吊著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.30,0:07:57.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  有本事你試試
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:02.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:03.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二宮同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.65,0:08:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  放我下來  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天的天氣就靠你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.70,0:08:17.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？難道春香姐姐樂在其中嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:21.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天不放晴不會放你下來的  加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我怎麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:25.29,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（交涉）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:27.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨雲先生  雨雲先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:30.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了  請一邊涼快去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.75,0:08:35.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像雨變大了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.73,0:08:37.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你惹怒雨雲怎麼行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要更尊重些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.06,0:08:40.56,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（交涉Ⅱ）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:45.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨雲先生  拜您所賜  大地已經得到了充分的滋潤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您差不多請回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.24,0:08:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨變小了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.77,0:08:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:56.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（交涉Ⅲ）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.33,0:09:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您一連工作三天三夜一定累了吧  雨雲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.75,0:09:05.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為防止水份不足  您稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停…停了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.18,0:09:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太神了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.23,0:09:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨過天晴真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.64,0:09:24.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能去海邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回再下雨就有勞你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.12,0:09:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:47.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是個晴天  真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:48.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.80,0:09:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎是多虧了千秋的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:52.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就準備好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.45,0:09:55.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們到客廳稍等一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:58.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.31,0:10:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨停了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於可以出發去海邊了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.17,0:10:07.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放我下來  我說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.41,0:10:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.09,0:10:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:10.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許問
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.07,0:10:13.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.72,0:10:15.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨雲別再來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.71,0:10:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最討厭你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  看你都做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨雲先生  十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.70,0:10:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才是說笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.64,0:10:29.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有人討厭您的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都非常喜歡您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.77,0:10:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許拜！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到海邊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.59,0:11:03.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.35,0:11:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太平洋算什麼  我們游個遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.79,0:11:16.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這想做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.33,0:11:17.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.48,0:11:18.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你問得出來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.13,0:11:22.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得我們替你選了件布料少的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你裹那麼嚴實做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.03,0:11:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不正為這個犯難嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.45,0:11:32.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看在千秋面上好歹是穿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:34.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但心理準備還是必要的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你快點來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.64,0:12:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害  你很拿手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.04,0:12:15.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香真慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.36,0:12:19.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去叫她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:28.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,付諸武力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:29.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.04,0:12:40.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想使蠻的也白搭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.47,0:12:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  又加了一件
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人很棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.10,0:12:47.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  誰是敵人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.07,0:12:50.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道她為什麼不脫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.18,0:12:52.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次換我來跟她談談吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.45,0:12:55.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.91,0:12:58.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得來到海邊  我們一起去游泳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.97,0:13:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:04.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我再考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:06.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  請慢慢考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.60,0:13:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.79,0:13:11.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼著她得想到天黑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.22,0:13:12.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  咱倆比比誰能讓她把外套脫掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:19.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北風和太陽嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:19.44,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（註：語出《伊索寓言》）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:21.09,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（太陽）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好刺眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:29.22,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（北風）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.81,0:13:33.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好涼快
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.30,0:13:35.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.47,0:13:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這反而讓她很舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.21,0:13:39.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那樣也好不到哪兒去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼之後只好用水潑她了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一來  她也就會投降了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:49.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  這樣只會讓她生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回她們又打的什麼鬼主意…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:57.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.61,0:14:00.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  果然是春香
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.56,0:14:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希  淳子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:05.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,速水學姐也來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.88,0:14:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真巧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.04,0:14:08.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是跟社團一起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.76,0:14:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們關係很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.33,0:14:14.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們在那邊打沙灘排球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香要參加嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:19.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我跟妹妹們一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:23.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很大膽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.34,0:14:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就顯得我自我意識過剩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不脫反而很怪的樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:32.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.79,0:14:34.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直目不轉睛地盯著我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:37.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就算是頑固分子的春香也…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:38.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那待會兒見
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.71,0:14:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.03,0:14:56.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  大家一起去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:05.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好豐滿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好豐滿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然  春香姐姐當然厲害了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:13.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  大家快來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:15.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:17.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.02,0:15:21.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:25.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們怎麼讓春香脫掉外套的？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.87,0:15:28.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  肚子好飽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.55,0:15:34.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便當真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:38.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  茶都喝光了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.38,0:15:38.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.16,0:15:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我去買些冷飲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.43,0:15:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.02,0:15:49.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就麻煩你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.45,0:15:55.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你這是做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有話和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.66,0:16:04.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼話能讓你妨礙我和春香姐姐一起去購物  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.08,0:16:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你腳底粘的沙子在我臉上擦著好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.93,0:16:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然覺得在你們間
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.56,0:16:16.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的價值似乎降低了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.42,0:16:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過就因為我沒能讓春香脫掉外套而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和這個無關
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你在我心中的價值依然在下降
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.46,0:16:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行時？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:30.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行時
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,STOP
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少說傻話了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在降到哪兒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:39.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才還差不多是這個水準
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:42.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在得是那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Beach Sandal{\r}\N拖鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.42,0:16:51.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的價值就和一隻丟棄的拖鞋一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.44,0:16:53.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要挽回名譽
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.22,0:16:56.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.70,0:17:00.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內田和吉野的家人既然把她們交給我們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們當然就得負責任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.20,0:17:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:06.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是溺水了之類就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.14,0:17:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我就準備了這玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.62,0:17:18.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣無論何時都能救她們
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.02,0:17:21.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的價值是無限的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:24.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無限的是你那蠢腦瓜子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:26.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以溺水為前提？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.00,0:17:29.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說這可是我的救生圈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:32.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.64,0:17:34.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是要做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:38.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上回是晴天娃娃  這回又讓我扮作海怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.02,0:17:38.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（註：原文「海坊主」，也可解作海龜）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:40.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼著能得到什麼恩惠？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說  海怪是個什麼視覺效果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:47.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野和內田若是溺水的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.99,0:17:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可得抓緊她們別鬆開哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.34,0:17:53.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把你們一夥兒全拉上來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.02,0:18:00.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想釣魚就乘漁船去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:02.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了  你滾一邊去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.26,0:18:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,套上這被丟棄的拖鞋滾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.86,0:18:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  這不是千秋嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.89,0:18:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人在做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.90,0:18:38.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香和夏奈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐去買東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.18,0:18:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許說得過了些
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:55.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.55,0:18:57.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？夏奈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.71,0:19:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈真是的  居然丟下千秋一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.44,0:19:06.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.16,0:19:07.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈她…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.20,0:19:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:11.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.53,0:19:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呵～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看  我找著了這麼大的貝殼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.35,0:19:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起海怪倒更像是河童的腦袋嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.67,0:19:25.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會在海裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.03,0:19:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回河裏去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.58,0:19:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算哪門子的挽回名譽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.40,0:19:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這豬頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.47,0:19:34.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南家三姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:38.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是吉野啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:42.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.65,0:19:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然從海邊回來被曬得通紅  火辣辣地疼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:50.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,曬得通紅的人將來會禿頂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.28,0:19:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.53,0:19:56.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話一點根據也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:20:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早就覺得千秋和姐姐們性格不一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於明天家政課…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.24,0:20:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我們會不像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.91,0:20:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.73,0:20:17.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要都像你那樣就了不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:19.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:21.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼  蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.04,0:20:24.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正所謂一觸即發呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:28.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是大家都像我一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.21,0:20:30.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.11,0:20:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:32.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.35,0:20:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好悠閒～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.67,0:20:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定會變成沒用的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.81,0:20:46.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是南家老二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.34,0:20:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是內田啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:51.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好  很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:55.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自從海邊回來後我脫了很多皮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脫太多皮的話會變矮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.68,0:21:00.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.39,0:21:04.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別信  我家老二是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.66,0:21:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋家真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:09.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一位有趣的姐姐和一位溫柔的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.03,0:21:12.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎每天都很愉快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.36,0:21:15.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  關於明天體育課…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著剛才的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.98,0:21:25.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為大家性格不同才那麼愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就非常喜歡性格不同的你們倆哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:34.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐  來吃點心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.15,0:21:35.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.38,0:21:39.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛  也算我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:47.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  張嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.27,0:21:48.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:55.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,河童
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.89,0:23:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨  阿珍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.13,0:23:32.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.97,0:23:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼笨蛋會無緣無故那麼興奮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.40,0:23:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  阿珍誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.40,0:23:40.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來  阿珍是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.80,0:23:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道就瞎叫喚嗎  蠢貨

